{"type":"message","id":"1520909f","parentId":"a315893d","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:45:00.884Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:investment-research-event-watch-0945 09:45来福投研会-临时会商监控] 执行以下任务：\n1. 进入 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\n2. 运行 python3 scripts/run_investment_research_event_watch.py\n3. 若 event watch 为 triggered，则继续运行 python3 scripts/generate_investment_research_temporary_meeting_broadcast.py\n4. 读取 event watch md/json；若已生成 temporary meeting broadcast，则优先读取该广播\n5. 如果 status=no_trigger，则回复 NO_REPLY\n6. 如果 status=triggered，则用中文简短汇报：触发项、是否建议临时会商、建议参与角色、temporary meeting broadcast 路径、event watch 路径\n7. 不要输出可执行买价\nCurrent time: Friday, April 3rd, 2026 — 9:45 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-03 01:45 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1775180700878}}
